1
00:00:00,781 --> 00:00:02,264
(owl hoots)

2
00:00:03,449 --> 00:00:06,651
(humming)

3
00:00:06,719 --> 00:00:08,069
(chuckles)

4
00:00:08,154 --> 00:00:08,903
(yelps)

5
00:00:08,971 --> 00:00:10,739
Why, you little...

6
00:00:10,806 --> 00:00:14,075
(both groaning)

7
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:17,429
Beneath this smile,
I'm in awful, awful pain!

8
00:00:17,496 --> 00:00:19,664
(screaming)

9
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:23,251
Welcome, precious
primetime viewers,

10
00:00:23,335 --> 00:00:27,422
valued Internet downloaders,
and scary digital pirates!

11
00:00:27,490 --> 00:00:30,258
If you want to shield
your little darlings

12
00:00:30,326 --> 00:00:33,244
from our stomach-churning
holiday special,

13
00:00:33,312 --> 00:00:36,080
simply hit fast-forward
on your DVR remote...

14
00:00:37,817 --> 00:00:40,084
(distorted grunting)

15
00:00:49,361 --> 00:00:50,678
I went too far!

16
00:00:50,746 --> 00:00:52,397
Spoiled the whole
show for everybody!

17
00:00:52,465 --> 00:00:55,450
I don't deserve
to wield the remote.

18
00:00:55,518 --> 00:00:57,702
(shuddering):
Oh, I'm getting old and gray...

19
00:00:57,770 --> 00:01:00,038
I'm dead.

20
00:01:00,105 --> 00:01:01,639
(spooky music plays)

21
00:01:03,592 --> 00:01:07,061
Monster go watch <i>The Office.</i>

22
00:01:07,129 --> 00:01:11,666
Dunder-Mifflin just like
monster's workplace.

23
00:01:11,734 --> 00:01:13,218
♪ ♪

24
00:01:23,496 --> 00:01:27,232
<font color="#00ff00">♪ The Simpsons 22x04 ♪</font>
